[PNG image data - 64x64 pixel art of a friendly robot companion with a rounded rectangular body, large expressive eyes, antenna with a small heart, and tiny wheels. Color palette uses warm coral red (#E85D4E) for the body, soft cream (#FFF8E7) for the face, teal (#4ECDC4) accents, and golden yellow (#FFD93D) for the heart. The robot waves with one articulated arm, conveying approachability and creative warmth. Created to represent the helpful, friendly nature of AI assistants in a nostalgic 8-bit style.]